9. Violations and Remedies:
   Any unauthorized use of the Licensed Material constitutes a material breach of this license and will result in automatic termination of rights granted herein. The Licensor reserves all legal rights and remedies in the event of any violation, including but not limited to claims for injunctive relief and monetary damages.

10. Severability:
